 of your heart, as you would Christ. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Col 3:22","book":"Col","chapter":3,"verse":22},{"label":"1Pt 2:18","book":"1Pe","chapter":2,"verse":18},{"label":"Php 2:12","book":"Php","chapter":2,"verse":12},{"label":"2Co 9:11","book":"2Co","chapter":9,"verse":11}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Lit according to the flesh"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Eph:6:6","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Don’t work only while being watched, as people-pleasers, but as slaves of Christ, doing God’s will "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 143:10","book":"Psa","chapter":143,"verse":10,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Pr 16:9","book":"Pro","chapter":16,"verse":9,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gl 1:4","book":"Gal","chapter":1,"verse":4,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Eph 1:9","book":"Eph","chapter":1,"verse":9,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" from your heart. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ps 143:10","book":"Psa","chapter":143,"verse":10},{"label":"Pr 16:9","book":"Pro","chapter":16,"verse":9},{"label":"Gl 1:4","book":"Gal","chapter":1,"verse":4},{"label":"Eph 1:9","book":"Eph","chapter":1,"verse":9}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Eph:6:7","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Serve with a good attitude, as to the Lord and not to people, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Col 3:23","book":"Col","chapter":3,"verse":23,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Col 3:23","book":"Col","chapter":3,"verse":23}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Eph:6:8","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"knowing that whatever good each one does, slave or free, he will receive this back from the Lord. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Eph:6:9","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"And masters, treat your slaves the same way, without threatening "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 4:29","book":"Act","chapter":4,"verse":29,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 9:1","book":"Act","chap